div1.p: UNITED STATES DISTRICT COURT WESTERN DISTRICT OF WASHINGTON NORTHERN DIVISION
In the Matter of the Application of Marie Robina Grayson alias Marie Robina for a Writ of Habeas Corpus ) No. 2780 ORDER WITHDRAWING EXHIBIT

Upon the oral motion of the Unite States Attorney: IT IS HEREBY ORDERED that the government may permanently withdraw respndent's exhibits introduced in evidence in the above entitled cause, the same being the files of the Bureau of Immigration.
Received the above exhibits this 29th day of April, 1915.
IN THE DISTRICT COURT OF THE UNITED STATES FOR THE WESTERN DISTRICT OF WASHINGTON. Northern DIVISION.
In the Matter of the Application of Marie Robina Grayson alias Marie Robina for a Writ of Habeas Corpus
FILED IN THE U. S. District Court, Western Dist. of Washington, Northern Division APR 29 1915
